text: The 1990 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1990 NCAA Division I-A football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by first-year head coach George Chaump. ==Schedule== ==Roster== *Not listed (missing number/class/position): Scott Zellem ==References== Navy Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy Midshipmen football
